<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="20.[189,1395,1421,2084]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[191,536,1934,1967]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Abundance and population size of the Davao Squirrel are not known, and there are no conservation measures in place.
</paragraph>
